Program Curriculum

Term 01: Product Management Fundamentals (6 Weeks)

Course 01 - Introduction to Product Management

  • Learn the basic frameworks of Product Management
  • Develop the skill of product sense
  • Master the art of first principles thinking

Course 02 - Product and UX Design

  • Learn the basic principles of product design
  • Develop the skill of designing wireframes and prototypes using Figma
  • Master the art of design thinking and innovation

Course 03 - Product Strategy

  • Learn the basic concepts of strategy
  • Develop the skill of writing product vision and strategy plans
  • Master the art of creating product roadmaps

Term 02: Software Product Management (6 Weeks)

Course 04 - Technical Product Management 101

  • Learn the basic lingo of software engineers and developers
  • Develop the skill of understanding technical processes in a product
  • Master the art of working with developers

Course 05 - Agile Product Management

  • Learn the basic values and principles of Agile
  • Develop the skill of writing epics and user stories
  • Master the art of building and managing PRDs

Course 06 - System Design and APIs

  • Learn the basic concepts of software and system design
  • Develop the skill of designing APIs for your product
  • Master the art of desgning LLDs and HLDs

Term 03: Data Product Management (6 Weeks)

Course 07 - Product Analytics

  • Learn the fundamentals of product metrics
  • Develop the skill of using analytical tools
  • Master the art of designing KPIs and metrics for your product

Course 08 - Data Analysis using SQL

  • Learn the fundamentals of Data Science and Databases
  • Develop the skill of fetching data using SQL queries
  • Master the art of making data-driven decisions for your product

Course 09 - Data Visualization for Product Managers

  • Learn the fundamentals of Data Visualization
  • Develop the skill of converting your data into beautiful visuals
  • Master the art of building product dashboards for your product

Term 04: Advanced Product Management (6 Weeks)

Course 10 - AI-ML Product Management

  • Learn the fundamentals of Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence
  • Develop the skill of using ML models, AI tools and Generative AI
  • Master the art of managing ML projects/products in your organization

Course 11 - No-code Product Development

  • Learn the basic usage of a no-code product development tool
  • Develop the skill of identifying a real problem and productionize it
  • Master the art of building and launching a product end-to-end

Course 12 - Global Product Certification Prep

  • Learn the basics of story estimation techniques
  • Develop the skill of managing product backlogs using Jira
  • Master the art of Scrum to crack your PSPO certification
